					<h1>WikiFax</h1>
					<p>Finding your way around Halifax has never been so easy. WikiFax is a light-weight, interactive map which can track it's user's location and updates them in real-time about their surrounds. All major Halifax data, including bus routing is included in WikiFax.</p>
